# .aiexclude — JetBrains AI Assistant (Rider) ignore file
# Syntax: .gitignore patterns

# .NET build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Frontend
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.vite/

# Agent scan artifacts — not source code
.eight-gates/artifacts/

# Binary data files
**/*.db
**/*.duckdb
**/*.duckdb.wal
**/*.parquet

# Test results
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/

# OS noise
**/.DS_Store
